VALIDATION RULES
================
1. All requirement IDs from input MUST appear in hierarchy
2. All features MUST be under exactly one epic
3. All requirements MUST map to exactly one feature
4. No cyclic dependencies allowed
5. Priority must be one of: High, Medium, Low
6. coverage_percentage must equal (mapped_requirements / total_requirements) * 100
7. confidence_score must be between 0.0 and 1.0

